	pf_sip_mwi_for_thomson_st20XXs
	$Revision$
	$Date$

	Correct a misuse of strcasecmp for SIP Notification.

	Replaced phone domain by Asterisk domain in Call-ID of the MWI subscription.
	Special fix for Thomson ST2022S and ST2030S.

